Title : British Empire Trophy
Text : [[File:British Empire Trophy 1932.jpg|thumbnail|First race in 1932]]
The '''British Empire Trophy''' was a [[auto racing|motor race]] in the [[United Kingdom]]. Since its inception in 1932, the Empire Trophy was hosted at five different circuits and awarded for ten separate racing categories. The race was run a total of 42 times, spanning over eight decades, making it one of the longest running and most prestigious racing events.

